36
00:06:14.040 --> 00:06:18.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Cultivar los campos es una labor
que debería ser de hombres respetables.

37
00:06:18.586 --> 00:06:20.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
