38
00:06:21.798 --> 00:06:24.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Esto no está bien.

39
00:06:24.425 --> 00:06:26.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aunque sean órdenes del señor…

40
00:06:26.928 --> 00:06:30.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Si se trata como iguales a los esclavos
y a los trabajadores del campo,

41
00:06:30.556 --> 00:06:33.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
se romperá todo orden social.

42
00:06:33.518 --> 00:06:34.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿No creéis?

43
00:06:43.778 --> 00:06:45.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Askeladd

44
00:06:46.072 --> 00:06:49.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
